rows.label: qst103311_msg0003
rows.name:
Her name is Saundra Arascain.
She is...was...a senator.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0005
rows.name:
Indeed. Her husband also sits
on the Senate, as I recall.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0006
rows.name:
Th-this is bad. This is a major incident.
I don't think I'm qualified to...

rows.label: qst103311_msg0007
rows.name: Sir! Sir, I need help here!

rows.label: qst103311_msg0008
rows.name:
Take her body to HQ and get
a field surgeon to look at her.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0010
rows.name:
Oh, and...I guess someone
needs to tell her family...

rows.label: qst103311_msg0012
rows.name:
I-if you're sure, ma'am.
It must be difficult...

rows.label: qst103311_msg0014
rows.name:
What an unhappy thing
to grow accustomed to...

rows.label: qst103311_msg0101
rows.name:
This woman is...
No, I have no idea who she is.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0102
rows.name:
It would take someone familiar with
Superbia or this area to identify her...

rows.label: qst103311_msg0103
rows.name:
I don't think we know anyone like that
right now. We might need to return to
this case later...
